 the moment, \r\n* the plugins are in the cloudsimd daemon, \r\n* the description is in inside/cgi-bin/common/machine_configuration.py \r\n* the widget layout is in cloudsim.js\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Adding a new constellation type should be as easy as adding a python file that contains:\n<em> The plugin methods (launch, terminate, monitor, start/stop sim)\n</em> the description of the constellation (for the launch selection menu)\n* the constellation machine and widget layout (seen in your browser)</p>\n<p>At the moment, \n<em> the plugins are in the cloudsimd daemon, \n</em> the description is in inside/cgi-bin/common/machine_configuration.py \n* the widget layout is in cloudsim.js</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Hugo Boyer", "uuid": "{3d87874e-7099-4981-b04f-57f0272faa7d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d87874e-7099-4981-b04f-57f0272faa7d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d87874e-7099-4981-b04f-57f0272faa7d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21198da8539b599e3633017f5f5f8150d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHB-6.png"}}, "nickname": "hugomatic", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:869c02bb-b246-4cdc-9db3-0064e8add185"}, "state": "duplicate", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-01-29T21:29:50.071927+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-02-13T01:54:31.951472+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 14}